  <brief_title>Efficacy of Azithromycin Prophylaxis in Preventing Recurrent Acute Sinusitis in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Azithromycin Prophylaxis in Preventing Recurrent Acute Sinusitis in Children : A Prospective, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo Controlled Trial.</official_title>
